dc_description_s: This data layer represents railroads for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2021.[This data depicts active rail lines. The location of the rail lines are derived from aerial orthophotography that meets national map accuracy standards at a scale of 1:2400. All lines are managed by Canadian National Railroad.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
